---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="👨‍💻 About Me - Manuel Gil - Software Developer & Open Source Advocate">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 pt-20">
    <section class="flex items-center justify-center py-32">
      <div class="max-w-3xl text-center">
        <h1
          class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent bg-clip-text text-6xl font-bold text-transparent"
        >
          About Me
        </h1>
        <p class="mb-8 text-xl text-zinc-400">
          Hi! I'm a passionate <strong class="text-zinc-200">Indie Maker</strong>, <strong
            class="text-zinc-200">Software Developer</strong
          >, and <strong class="text-zinc-200">Open Source Advocate</strong> with over 8 years of experience
          creating tools and apps that make life easier for developers and businesses. I specialize in
          <strong class="text-zinc-200">building open source tools</strong> that enhance developer workflows,
          like <strong class="text-zinc-200">JSON Flow</strong>, <strong class="text-zinc-200"
            >Auto Barrel for VSCode</strong
          >, and <strong class="text-zinc-200">Mustache Syntax Highlighting</strong>.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-8 text-xl text-zinc-400">
          Beyond coding, I contribute actively to the developer community, sharing knowledge through
          <strong class="text-zinc-200">talks</strong>, <strong class="text-zinc-200"
            >educational content</strong
          >, and <strong class="text-zinc-200">open source projects</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto mb-32 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold">🔥 My Mission</h2>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2 text-zinc-400">
          <li>
            🚀 <strong class="text-zinc-200">Empower developers</strong> by creating innovative <strong
              class="text-zinc-200">open-source tools</strong
            > that solve real-world development challenges.
          </li>
          <li>
            💡 <strong class="text-zinc-200">Educate and inspire</strong> by sharing insights, tutorials,
            and technical knowledge.
          </li>
          <li>
            🌍 <strong class="text-zinc-200">Support developer communities</strong> by contributing to
            <strong class="text-zinc-200"
              >open-source projects, organizing events, and mentoring</strong
            >.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a
          href="https://manuelgil.me"
          class="inline-block text-primary transition-colors hover:text-primary-dark"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Learn More About My Work →
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
